**Background:**
Scott Hardie is an accomplished educational innovator and strategic business leader with 15+ years of experience at McGraw-Hill and Pearson Education, driving 125% YOY sales growth through consultative selling, SaaS adoption, and strategic content design. He excels in creating engaging educational narratives, leading enterprise SaaS integrations, and delivering projects under budget and on time for diverse K-12 and adult learners.

**Recent AI & Automation Expertise:**
- Built Hardonia OS, a fully automated AI-driven Shopify commerce lab replacing 7+ apps with native AI workflows to run and scale eCommerce operations
- Created PromptPilot, a SaaS framework for orchestrating real-time prompt refinement and workflow automation
- Developed the Daily Intel Suite, 9 agents delivering TikTok, AliExpress, and consumer trend insights twice daily

**Education:**
